Q'orianka Kilcher https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Q%27orianka_Kilcher 0 Q'orianka Waira Qoiana Kilcher (born February 11, 1990) is an American actress, singer, and activist. She performed as Pocahontas in the 2005 film The New World, and Kaʻiulani in Princess Kaiulani.
